{"tid":759973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★點解條女咁開心？亡夫衣衫變咕𠱸貼身相伴　改造遺物助過渡哀傷","createTime":"2018-07-29T06:34:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T05:41:24.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ddfc1f3178caaa778e861a29664553a1248d8d1d","tid":759973,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T06:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1693386/org/eb2fcc8e987ed8b5e3217e5b43291aa0.jpg/YDRv07dRqT8HjpYD6_bDgIrOvUZLj12qT8DnYE_A52A?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1693386%2Forg%2Feb2fcc8e987ed8b5e3217e5b43291aa0.jpg%2FYDRv07dRqT8HjpYD6_bDgIrOvUZLj12qT8DnYE_A52A%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=7f4c3e6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n生死有命，靈魂離開，遺體霎眼腐化。亡者安息，回憶遠去，剩下的大堆遺物，卻令懷著巨大傷痛的親友每每睹物思人。面對遺物，有人選擇全部棄掉，逼令自己盡快接受現實；有人卻選擇將逝者所有東西原封不動，希望留著他活過的痕跡。本港有機構提供「遺物轉化」服務，透過專業輔導，了解死者遺物對其親友的意義，再由巧手工匠，將遺物改造成另一隨身物品，冷冰冰的遺物化成溫暖祝福，延續死者與生者的愛與關係，人不在，情永在。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/突發/215381/遺物轉化-死後-亡夫衣衫變咕𠱸貼身相伴-改造遺物助過渡哀傷\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC%2F215381%2F%E9%81%BA%E7%89%A9%E8%BD%89%E5%8C%96-%E6%AD%BB%E5%BE%8C-%E4%BA%A1%E5%A4%AB%E8%A1%A3%E8%A1%AB%E8%AE%8A%E5%92%95%F0%A0%B1%B8%E8%B2%BC%E8%BA%AB%E7%9B%B8%E4%BC%B4-%E6%94%B9%E9%80%A0%E9%81%BA%E7%89%A9%E5%8A%A9%E9%81%8E%E6%B8%A1%E5%93%80%E5%82%B7&d=l529D9%2FMuNwcFbTqbOpFY7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=2b69edbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/突發/215381/遺物轉化-死後-亡夫衣衫變咕𠱸貼身相伴-改造遺物助過渡哀傷</a>"},{"pid":"fc0da050d9ba56a4783a103ae73e9d7ba51e936b","tid":759973,"uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T06:35:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/143520_a7253303d870daaebe110686f740683d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F143520_a7253303d870daaebe1106